\id JUD Reconstructed from Ventura Publisher
\h Zut
\toc1 Khe Zut Khergi Gap
\toc2 Zut
\toc3 Zu
\mt1 ZUT
\mt2 Khe Zut Khergi Gap
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare.
\ip Kha gavar ki buni, nta maneŇč 2 Pitar ki buni fara muuŇčgi. Ana khuen guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ga suan za mbui. Mbe mba panan Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč ga kegi gumgi nzuai buni mbarara thari. Kha gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®va bavira, nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana ana nza n…®…®Ňčgi. Guma the nza kha khoth…®gi bigi, ana ntan kurarga tukt…®gi fhuvara.‚ÄĚ Ndu ves 3 gan…®ri.
\c 1
\ms1 Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, nde tuituigira ana gan…®v, nde mba Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč panan ne ga kegi gumgi nzuai buni, nde nta daaŇčgip, mbur kh…®ngiri.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Mt 13.55; Mk 6.3; Zo 17.11-12; 1 Pi 1.5\x*Gu Zut, gu Zisas Kraisan Ňčaara guma ma. Gu vh…®ra Zemsan Ňčguk ma. Gu kha gava khergiap, nde Fhe Bak…®me kamgi gumgi gu mbigi, gu anan nde ndi mbai. Fhe Bak…®me guigira wo ndavar nde nd…®…®im, Zisas Krais nduara nde gari.
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt 1 Pi 1.2; 2 Pi 1.2\x*Fhe Bak…®me nden kurarim, nde Fhe Bak…®me harigi gumgi kora mbui t…®v gum, ndava m…®…®t…®k gum, ana guigira won ndavar gumgi ga nd…®…®i t…®v, mba t…®vi, nta guigira havhargip nden k…®rim, nde mba t…®vir muuŇčri.
\s1 Panan Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč ga kegi gumgi, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigir vhen zergi.
\r 2 Pita 2.1-18
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Fi 1.27; 1 T 1.18; 6.12; 2 T 1.13; Ta 1.4\x*Nde nan k…®vntogi guari, gu kha gava kherav, gu khueŇč vuzvugi. Gu fharav, Fhe Bak…®me taagip nza ndir zav muuŇčgi Ňčaara bun nde suanga. Gu mba nd…®knd…®ga muuŇčgia thav, gu kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui. Gu ntigem harigi buni kher…®v, khaŇč mbe suanga, nde khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®va gan…®ri. Nde khaŇč t…®g…®p mba t…®va gan…®v, mba panan Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuueŇč ga kegi gumgi, nde mbe daaŇčgi mbur kh…®ngiri. Fhe Bak…®me nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana buna vhuuŇč bueŇčra nza n…®…®Ňčgi. Fhe Bak…®me nza suaŇčgi buna vhuueŇč, nza ne khoth…®gi, mba guma the ne dorg…® kh…®ngirga tukt…®gi fhuvara, ne mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Ga 2.4; Ta 1.16; Hi 12.15; 2 Pi 2.1; 1 Zo 2.22\x*Gumgi mbari, mbe wari vhaav zav, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigir vhen vergi. Mbe fhum guarara kha buni khergim, nta Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gavar ki. Mba khesharigi gumgi, mbe zumgum Fhe Bak…®me n…®man thivgirga, ana mbe suaŇčv suaŇčgirga, mbe fh…®ri reg…®rga. Mbe k…®r Fhe Bak…®me si gumgi ma. Mbe k…®r Fhe Bak…®me sav, anan kora muumbar mbe ana domdora suav, ana mbuim, mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi anan hi. Mba khesharigi gumgi, mbe nzan Guman Pana bavira, Zisas Krais, ana nza Bak…®me ma, mbe k…®r ana segi.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Kis 12.51; Nam 14.29-30; Sng 106.26; 1 Ko 10.5; 10.9; Hi 3.17-19; 2 Pi 1.12\x*Nde Guma Bak…®me kaŇčgi, ana fhum IsreriŇč ndigim, mbe Idz…®p thav vegi. Ana zumgum, guigira ana khoth…®gi fhuv gumgi gu mbigi, ana mben farfagi. Gu khueŇč vuzvugiap taagia nde nd…®knd…®gi khavi, nde taagi ne nd…®knd…®g…®rga. \f a \fr 1:5 \ft Mbe Grikar kaman khergi gavi vuri mbari, mbe khaŇč nzuai Guma Bak…®me. Mbe maaŇč nzuai fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara. Mbe khaŇč mbui kherar ana muuŇčgi, ‚ÄúZisas.‚ÄĚ \f*
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Zo 8.44; 2 Pi 2.4; 2.9; VB 20.10\x*Nde mba Fhe Bak…®me enseri ga nd…®knd…®g…®. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me mbe n…®…®Ňčgi Ňčaari, mbe tuituigip ntan k…® thav, mbe Fhe Bak…®me Ňčgu thagi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Guma Bak…®me zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki shenin mbe kegap, mbe ndim guigira g…®ng…®na mbat…®ga muuŇčgi Ňčgun phena t…®vaneŇč kh…®ngim, mbe mba Ňčgun ki. Mbe kav, Fhe Bak…®me kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga tuga bak…®men rarga mbur ki.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Stt 19.1-24; 2 Pi 2.6; 2.10\x*Fhum Sodom gu Gomora Ňčgu bak…®ni, manin han ki Ňčgui bak…®vi, ntan ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mbe muuŇčgi t…®vara muuŇčgi. Mbe t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbuav, mbe mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi guarira, mbe nta mbuav ruarir wari k…®…®i. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap mbe zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki zaa vhavar kav zaa ndi.
\p Khe fhum hegi bigi ma. Nza mba bigi ga nd…®knd…®g…®p, nza mbe muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, nza nta z…®n Ňčg…® tharga.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Kis 22.28; 2 Pi 2.10\x*Mba zav nden vhen zergi gumgi, mbe nde nd…®knd…®gi Ňčg…®r zav zegi. Mbe kha khesharigi t…®vi z…®n vui nt…®…®ri ma. Mbe mbark…®rga r…®…®a kuim, nta mbe nd…®knd…®gi khavim, mbe t…®vi mbat…®gi guarira wari won fhavi ga mbui. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, vh…®ra nza Guma Bak…®me ga r…®…®r…®…®v, mbe vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men enserir, mbe buni mbat…®gir mbe nzuai.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Lo 34.6; Dan 10.13; 10.21; 12.1; Sek 3.2; 2 Pi 2.11-12; VB 21.7\x*Mba Fhe Bak…®me enserir vhari Maiker, ana kamthoon Moses khuma nzuav Satan phorga shogap, ana dav, anan ndav shigi fhu. Ana vh…®ra buna mbat…®ga thuen Satan ga suaŇčgi fhu. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana fhura khaŇč ana nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me nduara ndu vheg…®p, kama havharar thini p…®n…® saŇčv ndu suanga.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 2 Pi 2.12\x*Mba buni mbat…®gi nzuai gumgi, mbe mba bigi n…®…®Ňčge kaŇčgiap, buni mbat…®gi nzuai fhuvara. Mba buni mbat…®gi nzuai gumgi, mbe kha nuianan ki s…®gi fara muuŇčgi, mbe nd…®knd…®gi ki fhuvara, mbe fhura rui. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, mben t…®vi guigira mben farfagi.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Stt 4.3-8; Nam 16.1-35; 22.1-35; 2 Pi 2.15; 1 Zo 3.12\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Fhe Bak…®me mben farfagirga. Mbe Kein muuŇčgi t…®va z…®n vui. Mbe Ňčk…®…®a nzuav mbuav, mbe Baram mbui t…®va mbui. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe Kora fara muuŇčgiap Fhe Bak…®me r…®…®Ňčr…®…®Ňčgi. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe guigira fh…®reregi.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Ese 34.8; Mt 15.13; 1 Ko 11.21; Ef 4.14; 2 Pi 2.13; 2.17; VB 2.11; 20.14\x*Nde zazera wari t…®gap phogi ga vhov mba mba shaa ga mbuav pav, nde khuen ndi kh…®vi. Nde ndava bavira kav, nde guigira wari won ndavir Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi ga nd…®…®i. Mba gumgi zav, Fhe Bak…®me n…®man t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui. Mbe mba shama bak…®men kav, pi ne fara muuŇčgiap pav, mbe nen mberi fhu, mbe warira nd…®knd…®gi. Mbe ph…®ga ndogiap, zav, nde han ki. Mbe mbok nzir zav mbui buiva ph…®givige fara muuŇčgi. Mba buiva ph…®givige fhura zim, b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč nta t…®gim, nta fhura tamtam vui. Mbe vh…®ra khira vh…®gi mbai tugen, mbe vh…®gi mbai fhu. Mbe vh…®ra guma th…®ri kh…®gap, kha sigim, ana sh…®…®Ňčgi fara muuŇčgi. Mbe fharav rimgip, wom r…®m…®nga gumgi ma.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Ais 57.20; Fi 3.19; 2 Pi 2.17\x*Mbe tamtam farfav mbas…®k phuri ra shogi fhara muuŇčgi gumgi ma. Mbe vh…®ra mberav t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui fhuvara. Mbe k…®rara thivgiap, mbas…®k purira shogim, ana phuvi huri k…®rara ki fara muuŇčgiap, mbe won t…®vi mbat…®gir nden t…® sui. Mbe vh…®ra mbu buivar ki Ňčkaar fara muuŇčgiap, mbe wari wo vui tuavir vui fhuvara. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me guigira g…®ng…®ngiap, guigira ph…®gi Ňčgu ana ana muuŇčgi, mbe anan Ňčgeg…®p, zazera mbara muuŇčgip anan k…®rga.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Stt 5.18-24; Lo 33.2; Dan 7.10; Sek 14.5; Mt 25.31; 2 Te 1.7; VB 1.7\x*Enok, ana Adaman harath…®gi nz…®ga mbe ma. Ana Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi nzuai suambara mbuav, ana mba gumgi mbat…®gir h…®rga bigeŇč ana ne bun suaŇčgi. Ana khaŇč suaŇčgi, ‚ÄúGu Guma Bak…®me garim, ana Fhe Bak…®me enserir vh…®rve guarira kov zi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Sng 31.18; 94.4; Mal 3.13\x*Ana za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suaŇčv muumbara mbat…®gar mben muuŇčgirga. Ana mba suaŇčgi t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…® thagi gumgi gu mbigi, ana guigira mben muuŇčgirim, mbe guigira wari wo muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi vheza ndigirga. Fhe Bak…®me guigira mba khesharigi gumgir muuŇčgirim, mbe guigira wari wo muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi gum mbe mba mbark…®rga buni mbat…®gir ana suaŇčgi, mbe guigira ntan vheza ndigirga.‚ÄĚ
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Snd 28.21; Ze 2.1; 2.9; 2 Pi 2.10; 2.18\x*Mba gumgi, mbe bigi mben him, mbe za ndavi shiav, buni vh…®rve nzuav, fhura bigir gumgi ga si. Mbe wo ndavi vherir ki t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe ntara z…®n vui. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe fhura sh…®sh…®gap kaa bak…®vi ga nzuav, wari wo z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuagi. Mbe maaŇč mbuav wari z…®n Ňčg…®r zav fhura gumgi raaŇč shi.
\s1 Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v nde ndavi havhargiri.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt 2 Pi 3.2\x*Nde nan fegi gu Ňčgugi, nde mba zumgum h…®r za mbui bigir kameŇč mbararagi, nde nta nd…®r…®g…®ri! Mba buni Zisas farasarigi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi fhum mba bigi bun nza suaŇčgi.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt 1 T 4.1; 2 T 3.1; 2 Pi 2.1; 3.3\x*Mbe fhum khaŇč nde suaŇčgi, ‚ÄúZisas taagip zir…®rga tuk han mbararga, Fhe Bak…®me nz…®…®v, guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi nz…®…®i buni nzuai gumgi heg…®rga. Mbe heg…®p, k…®r Fhe Bak…®me seg…®p, mbe won t…®vi mbat…®gira z…®n Ňčg…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Hos 4.14; 1 Ko 2.14-15; Hi 10.25; Ze 3.15\x*Mba gumgi, mbe Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi sh…®gap, mbe kha nuiana vuzvugi mbat…®gi z…®n vui. Mbe maaŇč mbuim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar mben ki fhu.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Ro 8.26; Ef 6.18; Kor 2.7; 1 Te 5.11; 1 T 1.4\x*Nde nan fegi gum Ňčgugi, nde zazera guigira Zisas khothivav, ana z…®n vui nd…®knd…®k guigira nde ndavi havhargiri. Nde mba Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, Fhe Bak…®me nduara mba t…®var nde n…®…®Ňčgi. Fhe Bak…®me Ňäina Ňäaar havharar nden n…®…®Ňčrim, nde Fhe Bak…®me phorg…® suaŇčri.
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Ta 2.13; 2 Pi 3.12\x*Fhe Bak…®me guigira won ndavar nde n…®…®Ňčgi, nde guigira anan hara k…®rim, ana zazera won ndavar nden n…®…®Ňčri. Nde k…®v, zazera nza wo Bak…®me Zisas Krais rarg…® k…®rim, ana guigira won kora muumbarar ndi k…®ra ph…®rarim, nde zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndigirga.
\v 22 Nde vh…®ra guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mba ana khoth…®gi t…®v havhargi fhu gumgi gu mbigi, nde mben korar muuŇčri.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Amo 4.11; Sek 3.2-5; Ro 11.14; 1 Ko 3.15; VB 3.4\x*Mbe mbari, mbe vhava r…®r za mbui fara muuŇčgi, nde vhemkora mben kurav, taagip mbe ndigiri. Mbe mbari, nde mben kora muuŇčv, nde vh…®ra mben riv…®ri. Mbe guigira ndava vurar kav, mbe guigira nzaŇčnzaŇčgi. Mben t…®vi mbat…®gi mben shagi ga muuŇčgim, nta vh…®ra nzaŇčnzaŇčgi. Nde Fhe Bak…®me n…®man mba nzaŇčnzaŇčgi t…®vi gum bigi, nde nta thav, samra k…®ri.
\s1 Nza Fhe Bak…®me z…® ndi vun kuamkuarga.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Ro 16.25; Ef 3.20; Fi 1.10; Kor 1.22; 2 Pi 3.14\x*Fhe Bak…®me nde gan…®nga, nde r…®g…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Ana vh…®ra nde ndigi Ňčg…®p, won Ňčgun vhuun Ňčg…®g…®rim, nde ana n…®man simt…®k thueŇč keg…®rga fhu, nde ana han k…®v, nde guigira ndikndig…®rga.
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Ro 16.27; 1 T 1.17; 2.3; 2 Pi 3.18\x*Nza mba Fhe Bak…® bavira ki. Ana kav, ana nduara nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais muuŇčgi Ňčaara panan, ana taagiap nza ndigi. Nza ne suaŇčv ana z…® ndiv vun kuamkuarga. Ana nduara Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pana vhari k…®rga. Ana ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me ki, ana za kha bigi gari guman pan k…®rga. Ana fhum zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki, ana vh…®ra ntigem mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga. Ana vh…®ra zumgum, ana zazera mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga. KhueŇč guigira.
